Package: xcmsViewerProcess
Type: Package
Title: Processing and annotating data for xcmsViewerApp
Version: 0.1.21
Date: 2020-03-01
Author: Chen Meng
Maintainer: Chen Meng <mengchen18@gmail.com>
Description: Converting MSnExp object to simple table format, including meta table and intensity. Identified features will be annotated if annotation information (monoisotopic mass and MS2 spectra) is given. The output is ready to be visualized using xcmsViewerApp.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: BiocParallel, MSnbase, dplyr, fastmatch, minpack.lm, reshape2, xcms, MAIT, utils, xcmsViewerApp, Biobase
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
